                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2002-10-21</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>I would say this book is a great look at software product management for professionals of all levels. The book stays true to its summary (see above) and is an overall great reference. Even though I have been a CTO for 6 years now, I found a lot in the book that was very useful. My staff also found the book very useful. I highly recommend this book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">First Rate-Must Read</div>
